This is what you look like
when there's no running water.

01:14.191 --> 01:16.793
- Again?
- Yes, again.

01:16.827 --> 01:18.528
I did tell you not to buy it.

01:18.596 --> 01:20.797
When it was an
apartment, it was perfect,

01:20.831 --> 01:22.766
and then it found out
it was becoming a condo,

01:22.800 --> 01:24.801
and then everything
started falling apart.

01:24.836 --> 01:26.636
You can have it for a cup of coffee.

01:26.671 --> 01:28.004
All right, come on.
We'll stop on the way.

01:28.039 --> 01:29.173
[ keys jingle ]

01:29.274 --> 01:30.874
That better be the building manager.

01:33.144 --> 01:34.811
Uh, hey, Jane.

01:34.845 --> 01:36.646
I thought you would be
gone [chuckling] by now.

01:36.680 --> 01:39.582
Why, because I've been waiting
for you since yesterday, Gilbert?

01:39.616 --> 01:43.052
Gil. [ chuckling ] Man.
Impatient, right?

01:43.086 --> 01:46.121
- She hasn't showered.
- Or had a cup of coffee.

01:46.155 --> 01:51.227
Please, tell me.
When did Boston join the third world?

01:51.261 --> 01:55.064
I have seven renters to keep happy.
Condo owners are last priority.

01:55.132 --> 01:56.565
You can always sell.

01:56.633 --> 01:59.001
You know what?
Don't start again with that, okay?

01:59.035 --> 02:00.735
Just get me some water ... please.

02:00.803 --> 02:03.738
I'll see what I can do.

02:03.839 --> 02:08.175
- Is that it?
- Yeah, that's it.

02:08.210 --> 02:11.179
W... was he just staring at my boobs?

02:11.213 --> 02:14.081
47% of men look at a woman's
breasts during a conversation.

02:14.149 --> 02:16.917
- Every time?
- It's unclear.

02:16.985 --> 02:18.819
[ door opens ]

02:18.853 --> 02:21.356
♪ If you were payin' by the
pound, I'd be a rich man ♪

02:21.390 --> 02:23.592
Why would you bring the poop inside?

02:23.659 --> 02:26.228
- Hey, Maura.
- Hello, Tommy.

02:26.262 --> 02:30.999
- Let's go.
- Just make sure that Gilbert skeevy

02:31.067 --> 02:32.267
doesn't go through my underwear.

02:32.335 --> 02:34.570
- Clean ones or dirty?
- Oh, my god, Tommy.

02:34.604 --> 02:36.572
Could you ... don't! 
Throw that away.

02:36.606 --> 02:38.240
Outside.

